definitions.definition: A reference book or electronic directory containing the photographs and names of various individuals .
A college publication distributed at the start of the academic year by university administrations with the intention of helping students become acquainted with each other.
examples: The shipment of facebooks will be distributed to the freshmen during orientation and move-in-week.
